OL,3,CMetal detectorist reunites WWI medal
OL,4,Cwith family of soldier
OL,6,FStephen continued: "I suspect what
OL,7,Fhappened is that he was attending a
OL,8,FRemembrance Sunday service.
OL,10,F"I think he was walking through the
OL,11,Ffield with his medal on and he's
OL,12,Feither tripped or fell because the
OL,13,Fmedal itself is not complete. It's
OL,14,Fonly the circular part of the medal
OL,15,Fand not the holder."
OL,17,FThere is still no picture of Nicholas,
OL,18,Fbut after weeks of searching, Stephen
OL,19,Fmanaged to track down his great niece
OL,20,FLisa and return the medal to her.
