OL,3,CMetal detectorist reunites WWI medal
OL,4,Cwith family of soldier
OL,6,FLisa Walmsley said: "It's an honour to
OL,7,Fbe contacted. People like Stephen are
OL,8,Fgiving us a lot back in terms of
OL,9,Fhistory and particularly when it's
OL,10,Fpeople that have fought for us in war,
OL,11,Fso I am thankful.
OL,13,F"Hopefully there maybe other family
OL,14,Fthat are more direct (to Nicholas)
OL,15,Fthat may come forward."
OL,17,FAlthough what Private Nicholas looks
OL,18,Flike remains a mystery, Stephen's
OL,19,Funcovered a piece of history, that has
OL,20,Fhelped bridge generations.
